Ending the weekend with a Maui Pineapple⁠ 🍍 ⁠
What beach would you want to enjoy this at?⁠
⁠
1 oz. Blue Chair Bay® Pineapple Rum Cream⁠
1 oz. blue curacao⁠
club soda⁠
orange, for garnish⁠
black salt, for garnish⁠
⁠
Combine Pineapple Rum Cream and blue curacao into a shaker. Shake vigorously. Strain into a glass filled with ice and top with club soda. Garnish with an orange wedge.

node.text:
Who needs a midweek pick-me-up?⁠
⁠
💛 Banana Cream Colada⁠💛⁠
⁠
🍌 2 oz. Blue Chair Bay® Banana Rum Cream⁠
🍍 1 oz. pineapple juice⁠
🍊 1 oz. orange juice⁠
🥥 1 oz. cream of coconut⁠
🧊 1 cup ice⁠
⁠
Add all ingredients to a blender. Blend until smooth. Add a banana slice and cherry for garnish.
